---
// Before/After email diptych for the Outbound value-prop block.
// Shows the AI-driven personalization in action.
// v1 placeholder: hand off to design for polish later.
---

<div class="ba-mock">
  <span class="ba-pill before">Before</span>
  <article class="ba-card before-card">
    <div class="ba-line">Hi <span class="ba-var">First name</span>,</div>
    <div class="ba-line">
      Saw that you <span class="ba-var">intent signal</span>. Specifically, you
      <span class="ba-var">AI Summary</span>.
    </div>
    <div class="ba-line">
      <span class="ba-var">Datapoint</span> usually
      <span class="ba-var">AI inferred problem</span>.
    </div>
    <div class="ba-line ba-faded">
      We solve this by <span class="ba-var">AI personalised value prop</span>.
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="ba-divider" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 80" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <line x1="12" y1="0" x2="12" y2="64" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 4" />
      <polygon points="7,64 12,72 17,64" fill="var(--color-accent)" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <article class="ba-card after-card">
    <header class="ba-after-head">
      <div class="ba-avatar" aria-hidden="true">LH</div>
      <div class="ba-from">
        <div class="ba-name">Lanny Heiz</div>
        <div class="ba-email">lanny@enablement.ch</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ba-time">9:14 AM</div>
    </header>
    <div class="ba-body">
      <p>Hi Hugh,</p>
      <p>
        Saw that you're <mark>hiring a marketing specialist</mark>. In the ad
        you mentioned improving <mark>conversion rates for your online store</mark>
        is key.
      </p>
      <p>
        Semrush estimates your traffic at <mark>~81,000 visitors/month</mark>,
        and on Shopify roughly 10% of shoppers abandon their carts.
      </p>
      <p>
        Usually, the AOV of a store like yours is around $75. That's about
        <mark>$15,000 in revenue missed every month</mark>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We solve this by helping online stores identify their shoppers and
        retarget them without spending more on ads.
      </p>
      <p>Can I send you the last 100 customers you missed - free?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-annotations">
      <span class="ba-anno">Find any datapoint</span>
      <span class="ba-anno">Summarise with AI</span>
      <span class="ba-anno">Write AI personalisations</span>
    </div>
  </article>
  <span class="ba-pill after">After</span>
</div>

<style>
  .ba-mock {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
  }
  .ba-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent-on);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .ba-pill.before {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: var(--space-4);
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .ba-pill.after {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: var(--space-2);
    right: var(--space-4);
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .ba-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  .before-card {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    margin-left: 0;
    width: 86%;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .ba-line + .ba-line { margin-top: 6px; }
  .ba-faded { opacity: 0.55; }
  .ba-var {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    background: var(--color-surface-raised);
    color: var(--color-body);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 1px 2px;
    vertical-align: baseline;
  }
  .ba-divider {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: var(--space-3) 0;
    height: 36px;
  }
  .ba-divider svg {
    height: 100%;
    width: 24px;
  }
  .after-card {
    margin-left: auto;
    width: 92%;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
  }
  .ba-after-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr auto;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    align-items: center;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .ba-avatar {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent-on);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .ba-name {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ba-email {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .ba-time {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .ba-body p {
    color: var(--color-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .ba-body p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .ba-body mark {
    background: rgba(225, 30, 72, 0.08);
    color: var(--color-heading);
    padding: 1px 3px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .ba-annotations {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
  }
  .ba-anno {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
    background: #1d4ed8;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>